item.title: About Me
item.description:
about me

Jeanette Raven

With nearly 20 years of design experience, I bring adaptability, creativity, and grit to solving complex problems. I unite cross-disciplinary teams around a shared vision, creating research-driven, customer-obsessed experiences that drive both customer and business success.

I thrive on inspiring and mentoring teams to think bigger and keep growing.

My special sauce? Bringing people together in collaborative sessions to innovate, challenge the status quo and deliver impact.
